{"title":"Radar Roundup: Standert Kettensäge, Blue Lug Belts, Ocean & San All Day Shirts, Restrap Frame Strap, Frontiers and Beyond, and Bikepacking Crystal Cove State Park","link":"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-standert-kettensage-blue-lug-belts-ocean-san-all-day-shirts-restrap-frame-strap-frontiers-and-beyond-and-bikepacking-crystal-cove-state-park/","date":1684416436000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Our Radar Roundup compiles products and videos from the ‘net in an easy-to-digest format. Read on below for today’s findings…<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1700\" height=\"1134\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike_1700.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike_1700.png?w=1700&amp;quality=75 1700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike_1700.png?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike_1700.png?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike_1700.png?resize=1335,891&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike_1700.png?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike_1700.png?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1700\" height=\"1134\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Cara.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Cara.png?w=1700&amp;quality=75 1700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Cara.png?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Cara.png?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Cara.png?resize=1335,891&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Cara.png?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Cara.png?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1700\" height=\"1134\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Baro.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Baro.png?w=1700&amp;quality=75 1700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Baro.png?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Baro.png?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Baro.png?resize=1335,891&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Baro.png?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Kettensage-Gravel-Race-Bike-Baro.png?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://standert.de/collections/kettensage\" target=\"_blank\">Standert Kettensäge Gravel Race Bike</a> €4.699</h3>\n<p>For the Kettensäge, Standert’s latest bike model, the brand took the racing DNA of the Kreissäge RS and its integrated cabling and translated it into a performance-oriented gravel racing chassis. The Kettensäge is the ultimate gravel race bike. Made in Italy from Dedacciai Aegis aluminium tubing, the Kettensäge comes with technical advantages that will make the difference.</p>\n<p>The UDH (Universal Derailleur Hanger) is designed to optimize shift performance as well as create a sensible solution for replacing damaged hangers. It’s becoming the standard and is available in almost every bike shop in the world.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Aegis Tubing in collaboration with our partner Dedacciai. State of the art light tubing, designed for racing and high performance aluminium bicycles.</p>\n<p>The tire width of choice for gravel races world wide is 700x40c but if you want you can fit up to 45c in the Kettensäge. As you’re going to have a good fueling strategy for gravel racing we help you out with mounts for a top tube snack bag.</p>\n<p>See the full build kit details, geometry, and breakdown at <a href=\"https://standert.de/collections/kettensage\" target=\"_blank\">Standert</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4401.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4401.jpg?w=1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4401.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4401.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4401.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/11_mg_8359_1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/11_mg_8359_1.jpg?w=1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/11_mg_8359_1.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/11_mg_8359_1.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/11_mg_8359_1.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4379.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4379.jpg?w=1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4379.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4379.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/1img_4379.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://global.bluelug.com/wears/belt.html\" target=\"_blank\">Blue Lug Quick Belt</a> $25.92</h3>\n<p>Blue Lug’s in-house branded products are always a big win and these Quick Belts look to be a great companion for summer time shorts, both on and off the bike. They come 47″ long and are made from Nylon webbing. The adjustment is a cinch, with an easy to use buckle, but perhaps the most appealing part of the Quick Belt is the variety of colors and patterns <a href=\"https://global.bluelug.com/wears/belt.html\" target=\"_blank\">Blue Lug offers at its international shipping webshop</a>!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\