ads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap7.jpg?w=1067&amp;quality=75 1067w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap7.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap7.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap7.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap7.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1067\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap10.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap10.jpg?w=1067&amp;quality=75 1067w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap10.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap10.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap10.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap10.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1067\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap11.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap11.jpg?w=1067&amp;quality=75 1067w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap11.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap11.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap11.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/00_Frame-Strap11.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://us.restrap.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Restrap Frame Strap Holds Your Spare Tube and More</a></h3>\n<p>Restrap’s Frame Strap is the perfect solution for carrying extra items and riding essentials on your bike. Ideal for mountain bikes or boosting the capacity of your current bikepacking setup.</p>\n<p>Made from grippy and hard-wearing Hypalon, the Frame Strap mounts securely to any part of the frame of your bike using fully adjustable velcro attachment to fit various sizes of tubing. Think of it as a beefier, more permanent version of our Fast Straps. It’ll allow you to firmly strap those extra items directly to the bike in a super secure package.</p>\n<p>Weight – 40g<br />\nRRP: £19.99 / €23.99 / $29.99</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://us.restrap.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Restrap</a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<div><span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4fDUglZ6Usg\" target=\"_blank\">Frontiers and Beyond</a></h3>\n<p>This film ‘Frontiers and beyond’ is the result of a day exploring the borders of Belgium and France, and the legendary cobbles of Paris-Roubaix. Watch as it follows the journey of Bert Stephani, a photographer and Fujifilm ambassador who has found a deep connection to the essence of gravel biking. With a love for frontiers and a passion for capturing the beauty in imperfection, he shares his experiences of navigating mixed terrain and overcoming the challenges of the cobblestones of Wallers Arenberg…</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HhjUzZynNmY\" target=\"_blank\">Bikepacking Crystal Cove State Park in Laguna Beach, CA</a></h3>\n<p>El Prado Racing Team embarks on an overnighter from Long Beach to Crystal Cove State Park as seen in Hi8mm.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Radavision</h3>\n<p>Stuff we see on the ‘net that causes pause…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Neuhaus-Hummingbird-29er-Review-8-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><i>Photo via <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/johnprolly/\" target=\"_blank\">@johnprolly</a></i></p>\n<p>Hailey’s Neuhaus Hummingbird review is on the way!</p>\n<p><em>If you’d like your photo featured in our Radar Roundup posts, tag us <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/theradavist/\" target=\"_blank\">on Instagram</a>!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-standert-kettensage-blue-lug-belts-ocean-san-all-day-shirts-restrap-frame-strap-frontiers-and-beyond-and-bikepacking-crystal-cove-state-park/\">Radar Roundup: Standert Kettensäge, Blue Lug Belts, Ocean &amp; San All Day Shirts, Restrap Frame Strap, Frontiers and Beyond, and Bikepacking Crystal Cove State Park</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"6d6a4d34bda7ca11c0eaa96e85fcaa2cf1c592940940789a741742f1f41ee0e0","category":"Cycling"}